mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From The Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "on The Record and Record Report", "Overseas Square Dance Dateline in Pictures", "As I See It By Bob Osgood", "National Convention News", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "A Square Dance People to People Project in Portland, Oregon", "Report-news of Worthwhile Caller's Association Projects", "Changes, Progress and You!!!", "Style Series: Ladies Center and the Gents Sashay Triple Allemande", "Big Time Caller", "Round The Outside Ring", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Ted Vaile", "Paging the Roundancers: Dave and Martha Martin", and "Experimental Lab: Dixie Spin".
